h3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ACB-R5S5omXMJsg40qZl2_OkdVfe57VxxJ8HnvZ6nxdsetw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 1 mes","text":"Excelente servicio. La chica que me atendió se llama Míriam, fue muy amable y atenta. Recomiendo esta tienda.","time":1679567734,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Toñi Ruiz","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118039954219744319218/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxYQLN1mpSINMRA0LY_ic8tZgk4o8fU5CeUe0BM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 meses","text":"Sin duda la atención es maravillosa, las chicas me trataron genial, además de que son muy profesionales,  lo recomiendo 100%","time":1679172953,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Juan Francisco Cano","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100671766414356245236/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AGNmyxbYAuuzV_hKQPCtotzjYwGklDcpq6bqGRb5WGY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 1 mes","text":"Estoy muy contento. Necesitaba vender unas piezas de oro y me han ayudado y asesorado perfectamente. Natalia, la chica que me ha atendido, muy profesional y me lo ha explicado todo genial. Gracias","time":1681409859,"translated":false}],"types":["jewelry_store","point_of_interest","finance","store","establishment"],"url":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=1948299470023102457","user_ratings_total":312,"utc_offset":120,"vicinity":"Plaza Juan XXIII, 76, Cartagena","website":"https://quickgold.es/tiendas/compro-oro-cartagena/plaza-juan-xxiii-76/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=boton&utm_content&utm_campaign=sitio-web-gmb","wheelchair_accessible_entrance":true},"status":"OK"},"general":{"acf":{"telefono":"912 29 68 55","meta_titulo":"Quickgold Alcobendas | Compro oro, empeños y cambio de divisa","meta_descripcion":"Tienda Quickgold en C/ 